game.description:
Like many others, you keep searching for a place where you can have a lot of fun during your vacant periods. If you are in such a mood, then you must play this beautifully-crafted adventure game – Varsity Stacey. You will definitely come to our website again and again if you try it at least once in any of your gaming device – be it a PC, a mobile or a gaming console. In this brand new flying game, you will have to drop to move Toss Stacey into the air and perform different types of challenging stunts. Drop those pom poms now and get yourself ready to fly in a beautiful sky!

It is easy and simple to perform stunts with the help of ASD. Use the space key to throw while the proper usage of arrow keys will help you to move Stacey into the air. Make sure you fly perfectly and do some cheerleading stuns to gain extra bonus points. This will ensure to add a significant sum of money to your wallet. Collect this cash, move to the store and upgrade your stunts so that you can fly even higher in the advanced level of this cool html5 game. 

The higher you fly and perform maximum cool stunts, the bigger points will be added to your wallet of cash. Good luck friends to soar even higher in this one of the best adventure games for boys!
